### Accessibility Patterns

**Color Contrast** (WCAG 2.2 AA):
- Text (small, <18.66px): ≥4.5:1 contrast ratio
- Text (large, ≥18.66px): ≥3:1 contrast ratio
- UI components: ≥3:1 contrast ratio
- Tool: Use WebAIM Contrast Checker

**Example Contrast Checks**:
- `text-slate-900` on `bg-stone-100`: ✓ 13.5:1 (excellent)
- `text-slate-700` on `bg-white`: ✓ 5.4:1 (pass)
- `text-slate-500` on `bg-white`: ✗ 3.1:1 (fail for small text)

**Touch Targets** (WCAG 2.5.5):
```tsx
// Minimum 44px × 44px (iOS/WCAG guideline)
<button className="min-w-[44px] min-h-[44px] p-3">
  <Icon className="w-6 h-6" />
</button>

// Spacing between targets (avoid mis-taps)
<div className="flex gap-4">
  <button>Action 1</button>
  <button>Action 2</button>
</div>
```

